caller_intent: The caller left a voicemail requesting a callback, but the subsequent outbound call from Brandi with Alliance Insurance was a follow-up regarding an email sent to National General, aiming to clarify contact information.
resolution_steps: Brandi confirmed the email was sent to National General and clarified it should not be directed to Alliance Insurance.
Provided the correct contact number for Alliance Insurance.
knowledge_required: Email routing between carriers and agencies
summary: An outbound call from Alliance Insurance followed up on an email sent to National General, clarifying contact information and providing a callback number. The initial voicemail was non-substantive, but the subsequent interaction was a service follow-up.
